{"tid":1456020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日機場必須撤退","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:38:09.000Z","uid":154808,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d14d2b19349563a3450ab20f686240a338d1e54f","tid":1456020,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"機場所以航班已經取消哂，機管局既員工同入境都提早收工，淨底既全部都係示威者，跟本就佢地就想困獸鬥，一cut上網同封橋就等收皮，手足們，冇車都要行去東涌，一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日目標已經達成，擇日再戰啦，一星期發一次夢都好正常姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5399f088d049a639c611469f545eb034027920","tid":1456020,"uid":113784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n留低有咩做？？自己問下自己。<br />\n<br />\n到時機場回復運作咪再入過囉，更加唔好講夜晚收工接力的手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0db4e774c4f876d8c0be1944f040680fa793d8","tid":1456020,"uid":251186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"其實成個做決定既過程好簡單，唔明有咩咁難諗<br />\n走：你有可能失去d乜<br />\n唔走：你有可能失去d乜<br />\n<br />\n我就咁睇，走左如果冇清場只係放流料，你咪蝕左一晚坐少左一晚<br />\n唔走如果真清場，開槍又好棍毆又好，你有機會受傷被捕甚至死<br />\n<br />\n咁個考量已經好簡單，你唔怕受傷唔怕被捕唔怕死，咪繼續留低囉"},{"pid":"eedb88474dea33edd99dfcc28f941679baf087bf","tid":1456020,"uid":99384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"明天請早"},{"pid":"3d64adfb3ea8d5e3b1b92cc15de38e96e2ea7e87","tid":1456020,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"afe598c